{"tid":691102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請教報復玩殘仆街的士佬嘅方法","createTime":"2018-06-05T11:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T12:36:38.000Z","uid":119736,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ba6ff74445e1eb458e98ae6bd4ea1e27b20d650","tid":691102,"uid":119736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 大佬要返夜更, 因為住得偏冇車到, 日日焗住要凌晨搭的士返歸<br />\n<br />\n話說今朝佢如常返歸啦, 一返到嚟發哂爛渣係度掟野, 嘈住我打芒亨<br />\n<br />\n一問之下, 原來係俾個的士佬屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事源就咁, 本身佢搭開, 一早準備左24蚊落車果陣俾, 點知個的士佬兜路搞到跳左幾下錶<br />\n<br />\n咁佢諗住橫掂身上有散銀就摷埋出嚟埋佢啦咁, 摷左一陣就俾個的士佬爆粗催佢快撚啲<br />\n<br />\n雖然條氣好唔順, 最後佢都忍住冇出聲, 索性俾張50蚊叫佢找算<br />\n<br />\n點知落左車之後, 個的士佬仲要勁仆街, 特登挍低車窗勁大聲鬧佢「真係抵你俾人屌呀!」之後先開車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家都知返夜嘅人火氣特別大, 之前都試過一次又係個的士佬好鬼串, 結果我大佬的左佢落車打左一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 俾人捉到, 搞到今日都仲守緊行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次佢雖然忍到冇打人, 但就好明顯下唔到啖氣, 長遠嚟講都唔係辦法, 容乜易下次揾我嚟出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上我自己都試過遇着呢啲賤格的士佬, 多少都有啲怨氣<br />\n<br />\n想問下如果下次又遇到呢啲咁仆街嘅的士佬, 有咩方法對付<br />\n<br />\n最好係有啲方法可以當面晒冷, 迫個的士佬道歉, 咁就可以出氣之餘又唔駛花時間搞手續<br />\n<br />\n另外, 見到有啲投訴的士嘅form可以填,<a href=\"https://www.tcu.gov.hk/chi/taxi/index.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tcu.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ftaxi%2Findex.htm&d=NsE7wDIgqlO59o5HwdL980bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3503aa67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tcu.gov.hk/chi/taxi/index.htm</a><br />\n係咪真係有用架?"},{"pid":"95134f71eada39c5189648b558686767ab75cf12","tid":691102,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"人都走左仲可以做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f596ed00b5903503d9956135007d2f7c206b44ed","tid":691102,"uid":119736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95134f71eada39c5189648b558686767ab75cf12","tid":691102,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"人都走左仲可以做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"所以就係話<span style=\"color: red;\">下次</span>吖嘛"},{"pid":"9c829d910f7a6dabe9126f2347dfd339524b2cf9","tid":691102,"uid":158813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:20:01.000Z","msg":"響佢部車入面瀨尿"},{"pid":"bd7d50995928f3fd2b780a2a5c6cb810cdbf43c6","tid":691102,"uid":922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c829d910f7a6dabe9126f2347dfd339524b2cf9","tid":691102,"uid":158813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:20:01.000Z","msg":"響佢部車入面瀨尿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:33:31.000Z","msg":"如可轉瀨屎就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c83b8f5d30f91a9c1e6d9580b28fe604f8ff5d6","tid":691102,"uid":42055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"找錢要佢找足，唔足就報警"}]}